---
title: Home
description: My name is Daniel Hudson, I am a web developer based in the Gloucester and Cheltenham area.
layout: base.njk
---

<div class="container-wide">
    <p data-color="brand">Hello there, i'm</p>
    <h1 data-variation="hero">Daniel Hudson <br />I'm a <span data-color="brand">Web Developer</span></h1>

    <div class="grid" data-variation="col-50">

        <div class="column">

            <p>I'm a seasoned Web Developer with 8 years of expertise in creating engaging user interfaces and interactive web applications, I have a proven track record of delivering visually appealing websites with seamless user experiences.</p>
            <p>With a deep understanding of HTML, CSS, and JavaScript, I am skilled in creating responsive and accessible websites that work well on all devices.</p>

            <p><a class="button" href="/about-me/">About me</a><a class="button" href="/blog/">Blog</a></p>

            <h2 class="h3">Latest from my blog</h2>
            <ul class="featured-blogs">
                {% set homeblogposts = collections.post | sortByDate | limit(5) %}
                {%- for post in homeblogposts -%}
                <li>
                    <a href="{{ post.url }}">{{ post.data.title }}</a>
                    <time datetime="{{ post.data.date }}">{{ post.data.postDate }}</time>
                </li>
                {%- endfor -%}
            </ul>
            <p><a class="button" href="/blog/">View all posts</a></p>

        </div>

        <div class="column text-align--center">

            <picture>
                <source srcset="/assets/images/daniel-hudson-front-end-developer.webp" type="image/webp" />
                <img src="/assets/images/daniel-hudson-front-end-developer.jpg" width="837" height="837" alt="Web Developer Daniel Hudson" />
            </picture>

        </div>

    </div>

    <h2>Services</h2>

    <div class="[ feature-grid ] [ grid ]" role="list">

        {% for page in collections.servicesPages %}

            <div class="feature">

                <h3><a href="{{ page.url }}">{{ page.data.title }}</a></h3>

                <p>{{ page.data.shortDescription }}</p>

                <div>
                    <a class="button" data-variation="primary" href="{{ page.url }}">Read more</a>
                </div>

            </div>

        {% endfor %}

    </div>

</div>
